    ('BUS-C 205', 'BUSINESS WRITING: HONORS', '1226', 'Closed', 'MW Monday, Wednesday 9:35 AM–10:50 AM', 'HH 3046', 'Miranda Rodak', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'HODGE HALL (BUSINESS SCHOOL)', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'The overall goal of this course is to develop an awareness of the complexity involved in the communication process in order to communicate effectively both verbally (orally and in writing) and nonverbally in a business setting. The C205 capstone experience is participatation in a team case competition.', ARRAY['Class uses IU eTexts'], NULL),
